{"tid":738315,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Davis Bertans同意與馬刺隊簽下2年1450萬美元的續約合約","createTime":"2018-07-11T12:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T12:18:52.000Z","uid":5886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e351bc04e2a6535a29d0540a7fd855ed5bb1b8","tid":738315,"uid":5886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:18:52.000Z","msg":"Fox San Antonio記者Chuck Miketinac報導，Davis Bertans經紀人Happy Walters表示，與馬刺達成協議之前還有其他球隊也對Bertans有興趣，其中一支球隊甚至開出均薪更高的報價搶人，但是Bertans認為留在馬刺對長期發展最好，因此遲遲沒簽下來自其他球隊的報價合約。<br />\n<br />\nDavis Bertans稍早以2年14.5M與馬刺達成協議。根據此前消息，爵士、灰狼、籃網都有興趣簽下Bertans。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MaxSportsSA/status/1016870424590856192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMaxSportsSA%2Fstatus%2F1016870424590856192&d=0RoAtFcd%2FKvjBHT0hgqWWLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=e6d5f787\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMaxSportsSA%2Fstatus%2F1016870424590856192&h=24f73780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MaxSportsSA/status/1016870424590856192</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}